<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nexa | Link Discord</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --p: #00d2ff; --bg: #050505; --card: #0d0d0d; }
        body { 
            background: var(--bg); 
            color: white; 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            height: 100vh; 
            margin: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #101015 0%, #050505 100%);
        }
        .container { 
            background: var(--card); 
            padding: 50px 40px; 
            border-radius: 24px; 
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a; 
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px; 
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .discord-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #5865F2;
            background: rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.1);
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            line-height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
        }
        h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
        p { color: #888; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 35px; line-height: 1.6; }
        
        .btn-discord { 
            background: #5865F2; 
            color: white; 
            border: none; 
            padding: 16px 24px; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-discord:hover { 
            background: #4752c4; 
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.4);
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: #444;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .back-link:hover { color: var(--p); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="discord-icon">
            <i class="fab fa-discord"></i>
        </div>
        <h2>Satu Langkah Lagi!</h2>
        <p>Email berhasil diverifikasi. Sekarang, hubungkan akun Discord kamu untuk mengakses Nexa Quantum Dashboard.</p>
        
        <a href="/login" class="btn-discord">
            <i class="fab fa-discord"></i>
            CONNECT DISCORD
        </a>

        <a href="/" class="back-link"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Kembali ke Login Email</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
